1. *Afera* oko pronevere javnih sredstava je dovela do ostavke gradonačelnika. (Scandal* involving embezzlement of public funds led to the mayor's resignation.)
2. Oni su pokušali da prikriju *aferu*. (They tried to cover up the *scandal*.)
3. Ova *afera* je privukla pažnju medija. (This *affair* has attracted media attention.)
4. Glavni akteri u *aferi* su uhapšeni. (The main actors in the *affair* were arrested.)
5. *Afera* je uticala na imidž kompanije. (The *scandal* has affected the company's image.)
6. On je bio umešan u *aferu* koja se dogodila pre pet godina. (He was involved in an *affair* that happened five years ago.)
7. Tužilaštvo je pokrenulo istragu o ovoj *aferi*. (The prosecutor's office launched an investigation into this *affair*.)
8. Neki političari pokušavaju da iskoriste ovu *aferu* u svoju korist. (Some politicians are trying to use this *affair* to their advantage.)
9. Kompanija je izgubila mnogo novca zbog ove *afere*. (The company lost a lot of money because of this *scandal*.)
10. Ovaj *afera* je bila na naslovnoj strani novina nedeljama. (This *affair* was on the front page of newspapers for weeks.)